msgstr ""
"Rajoita pääsy :ref:`kauppaan <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` ja "
":ref:`kassalle <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` tietyille "
"asiakkaille, esim. :doc:`B2B <../ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c>`-"
