#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:5
msgid ""
"In Odoo's e-commerce workflow, an online purchase typically goes through "
"three main steps: :ref:`sale <ecommerce/handling/sales>`, :ref:`delivery "
"<ecommerce/handling/delivery>`, and :ref:`invoicing <ecommerce/handling/"
"invoices>`. Each step generates key documents, including sales orders upon "
"order confirmation, delivery orders to manage :doc:`picking </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"picking_methods>`, :doc:`packing </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack>`, and :doc:`shipping "
"<shipping>`, and invoices. Odoo eCommerce also offers additional tools to "
"send :ref:`abandoned cart emails <ecommerce/handling/abandoned_cart>`, "
"ensure :ref:`stock availability <ecommerce/handling/stock-management>`, and "
"handle product :ref:`returns and refunds <ecommerce/handling/returns>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoon verkkokaupan työnkulussa verkko-osto käy tyypillisesti läpi kolme "
"päävaihetta: :ref:`myynti <ecommerce/handling/sales>`, :ref:`toimitus "
"<ecommerce/handling/delivery>` ja :ref:`laskutus <ecommerce/handling/"
"invoices>`. Jokainen vaihe luo keskeiset asiakirjat, mukaan lukien "
"myyntitilaukset tilausvahvistuksen yhteydessä, toimitustilaukset "
":doc:`keräilyn </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"picking_methods>`, :doc:`pakkaamisen </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack>` ja "
":doc:`lähetyksen <shipping>` hallintaan sekä laskut. Odoo Verkkokauppa "
"tarjoaa myös lisätyökaluja :ref:`hylättyjen ostoskorien sähköpostien "
"<ecommerce/handling/abandoned_cart>` lähettämiseen, :ref:`varaston "
"saatavuuden <ecommerce/handling/stock-management>` varmistamiseen ja "
"tuotteiden :ref:`palautusten ja hyvitysten <ecommerce/handling/returns>` "
"käsittelyyn."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:20
msgid "Sale"
msgstr "Myynti"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:22
msgid ""
"To view all quotations and orders, navigate to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Orders`, and select one to open it. The status bar at the top "
"of the order shows its current status:"
msgstr ""
"Nähdäksesi kaikki tarjoukset ja tilaukset, siirry kohtaan "
":menuselection:`Verkkosivu --> Verkkokauppa --> Tilaukset` ja valitse yksi "
"avataksesi sen. Tilauksen yläosassa oleva tilapalkki näyttää sen nykyisen "
"tilan:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:25
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quotation`: A product has been :ref:`added to the cart <ecommerce/"
"checkout/add-to-cart>`, but the customer has not yet completed "
"the :ref:`checkout process <ecommerce/checkout/steps>`. If the customer is "
"not logged in, the quotation is assigned to the default *Public User* "
"contact."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tarjous`: Tuote on :ref:`lisätty ostoskoriin <ecommerce/checkout/"
"add-to-cart>`, mutta asiakas ei ole vielä suorittanut :ref:`kassaprosessia "
"<ecommerce/checkout/steps>`. Jos asiakas ei ole kirjautunut sisään, tarjous "
"määritetään oletusarvoiselle *Julkinen käyttäjä* -yhteystiedolle."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quotation Sent`: The customer has completed the :ref:`checkout "
"process <ecommerce/checkout/steps>` and confirmed the order, but "
"the :ref:`payment <ecommerce/checkout/payment>` has not yet been confirmed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tarjous lähetetty`: Asiakas on suorittanut :ref:`kassaprosessin "
"<ecommerce/checkout/steps>` ja vahvistanut tilauksen, mutta :ref:`maksua "
"<ecommerce/checkout/payment>` ei ole vielä vahvistettu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:32
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales Order`: The customer has completed the :ref:`checkout "
"process <ecommerce/checkout/steps>`, confirmed the order, and "
"the :ref:`payment <ecommerce/checkout/payment>` has been successfully "
"received."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Myyntitilaus`: Asiakas on suorittanut :ref:`kassaprosessin "
"<ecommerce/checkout/steps>`, vahvistanut tilauksen ja :ref:`maksu <ecommerce/"
"checkout/payment>` on vastaanotettu onnistuneesti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:37
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Confirmed` filter is enabled by default in "
"the :guilabel:`Orders` list. To view *all* quotations and orders, remove the "
"filter."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vahvistettu`-suodatin on oletuksena käytössä "
":guilabel:`Tilaukset`-luettelossa. Nähdäksesi *kaikki* tarjoukset ja "
"tilaukset, poista suodatin."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:39
msgid ""
"To view only orders in the :guilabel:`Quotation Sent` stage, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Orders` and remove "
"the :guilabel:`Confirmed` filter. Then, open the :icon:`fa-caret-down` "
"dropdown menu and, under :guilabel:`Filters`, select :guilabel:`Unpaid`."
msgstr ""
"Nähdäksesi vain tilaukset :guilabel:`Tarjous lähetetty`-vaiheessa, siirry "
"kohtaan :menuselection:`Verkkosivu --> Verkkokauppa --> Tilaukset` ja poista "
":guilabel:`Vahvistettu`-suodatin. Avaa sitten :icon:`fa-caret-down`-"
"pudotusvalikko ja valitse :guilabel:`Suodattimet`-kohdasta "
":guilabel:`Maksamaton`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:42
msgid ""
"E-commerce orders can be automatically assigned to a specific sales team or "
"salesperson. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. In the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section, under :guilabel:`Orders "
"Assignment`, select the relevant :guilabel:`Sales Team` "
"or :guilabel:`Salesperson`."
msgstr ""
"Verkkokauppatilaukset voidaan automaattisesti osoittaa tietylle "
"myyntitiimille tai myyjälle. Siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Verkkosivu --> "
"Asetukset --> Asetukset`. Osiossa :guilabel:`Verkkokauppa`, kohdassa "
":guilabel:`Tilausten osoitus`, valitse asiaankuuluva :guilabel:`Myyntitiimi` "
"tai :guilabel:`Myyjä`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:48
msgid ""
"This three-step process is not visible to customers. However, they can view "
"their orders and check their status through the customer :doc:`portal </"
"applications/general/users/user_portals>`."
msgstr ""
"Tämä kolmivaiheinen prosessi ei näy asiakkaille. He voivat kuitenkin "
"tarkastella tilauksiaan ja tarkistaa niiden tilan asiakkaan "
":doc:`portaalissa </applications/general/users/user_portals>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:51
msgid ""
"If the customer pays via :ref:`wire transfer <payment_providers/"
"bank_payments/wire_transfer>`, the quotation is *not* automatically "
"confirmed. In this case, the customer receives a notification on "
"the :guilabel:`My account` page of their :doc:`customer account "
"<configuration/customer_accounts>` to review and pay for the order. After "
"the payment is received, the order must be manually confirmed in the backend."
msgstr ""
"Jos asiakas maksaa :ref:`tilisiirrolla <payment_providers/bank_payments/"
"wire_transfer>`, tarjousta *ei* vahvisteta automaattisesti. Tässä "
"tapauksessa asiakas saa ilmoituksen :doc:`asiakastilinsä <configuration/"
"customer_accounts>` :guilabel:`Oma tili`-sivulla tarkistaakseen ja "
"maksaakseen tilauksen. Kun maksu on vastaanotettu, tilaus on vahvistettava "
"manuaalisesti hallintapuolella."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:58
msgid ":doc:`checkout`"
msgstr ":doc:`checkout`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:59
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:64
msgid "Abandoned carts"
msgstr "Hylätyt ostoskorit"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:66
msgid ""
"An abandoned cart is created when a customer adds products to the cart but "
"does not go through the :ref:`checkout process <ecommerce/checkout/steps>` "
"or leaves the website before completing it. It is possible to automatically "
"send an email reminder to the customer for these pending orders."
msgstr ""
"Hylätty ostoskori syntyy, kun asiakas lisää tuotteita ostoskoriin, mutta ei "
"käy läpi :ref:`kassaprosessia <ecommerce/checkout/steps>` tai poistuu "
"verkkosivustolta ennen sen loppuun saattamista. Asiakkaalle voidaan "
"automaattisesti lähettää sähköpostimuistutus näistä odottavista tilauksista."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:70
msgid "To enable abandoned cart reminders:"
msgstr "Hylättyjen ostoskorien muistutusten käyttöönotto:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:73
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section, enable :guilabel:`Follow up abandoned "
"carts`."
msgstr ""
"Osiossa :guilabel:`Verkkokauppa` ota käyttöön :guilabel:`Seuraa hylättyjä "
"ostoskoreja`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:74
msgid ""
"Set the time delay after which the reminder email is sent in "
"the :guilabel:`Send after` field, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Aseta aikaviive, jonka jälkeen muistutussähköposti lähetetään, kenttään "
":guilabel:`Lähetä ajan kuluttua`, ja napsauta sitten :guilabel:`Tallenna`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:76
msgid ""
"If needed, click the :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Customize Abandoned "
"Email Template` link to customize the :doc:`email template </applications/"
"general/companies/email_template>`."
msgstr ""
"Tarvittaessa napsauta linkkiä :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Muokkaa "
"hylätyn ostoskorin sähköpostimallia` muokataksesi :doc:`sähköpostimallia </"
"applications/general/companies/email_template>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:79
msgid ""
"To view all abandoned carts, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Orders` and remove the :guilabel:`Confirmed` filter. Open the :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down` dropdown menu and, under :guilabel:`Filters`, "
"select :guilabel:`Abandoned`."
msgstr ""
"Kaikkien hylättyjen ostoskorien tarkastelemiseksi siirry kohtaan "
":menuselection:`Verkkosivu --> Verkkokauppa --> Tilaukset` ja poista "
"suodatin :guilabel:`Vahvistettu`. Avaa :icon:`fa-caret-down` pudotusvalikko "
"ja valitse kohdasta :guilabel:`Suodattimet` vaihtoehto :guilabel:`Hylätty`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:84
msgid ""
"To receive reminders, customers must have entered their contact details "
"during checkout or be logged in when adding items to the cart. Without the "
"customer details, it remains a :ref:`quotation <ecommerce/handling/sales>` "
"with no follow-up."
msgstr ""
"Muistutusten vastaanottamiseksi asiakkaiden on täytynyt syöttää "
"yhteystietonsa kassalla tai olla kirjautuneena sisään lisätessään tuotteita "
"ostoskoriin. Ilman asiakkaan tietoja se säilyy :ref:`tarjouksena <ecommerce/"
"handling/sales>` ilman seurantaa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:87
msgid ""
"Abandoned cart reminders are only sent for carts created after the feature "
"is enabled. Existing abandoned carts are not affected."
msgstr ""
"Hylättyjen ostoskorien muistutuksia lähetetään vain ostoskoreille, jotka on "
"luotu ominaisuuden käyttöönoton jälkeen. Olemassa olevat hylätyt ostoskorit "
"eivät ole mukana."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:96
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Inventory app </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` must be "
"installed to process deliveries."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Varastointi-sovellus </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` on "
"asennettava toimitusten käsittelemiseksi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:98
msgid ""
"Delivery orders are not generated for :guilabel:`Service` "
"or :doc:`subscription </applications/sales/subscriptions>` products."
msgstr ""
"Toimitustilauksia ei luoda :guilabel:`Palvelu`- tai :doc:`tilaustuotteille </"
"applications/sales/subscriptions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:101
msgid ""
"Once a sales order is confirmed, a delivery order is automatically created. "
"To access it, click the :icon:`fa-truck` :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button "
"on the sales order."
msgstr ""
"Kun myyntitilaus on vahvistettu, toimitustilaus luodaan automaattisesti. "
"Päästäksesi siihen, napsauta myyntitilauksen älypainiketta :icon:`fa-truck` "
":guilabel:`Toimitus`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:104
msgid ""
"The next step is preparing e-commerce orders in the warehouse. Depending on "
"order volume, refill and stock management strategies, or available "
"resources, different :doc:`stock handling flows for receipts and deliveries "
"</applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"daily_operations>` can be implemented. These flows may involve manually "
"receiving, :doc:`picking </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/picking_methods>`, and :doc:`packing </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"multipack>` products, printing :doc:`shipping labels </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels>`, "
"and :doc:`shipping  <shipping>` orders to customers, or handling these "
"processes through :doc:`dropshipping </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping>` "
"or :doc:`consignment flows </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock>`."
msgstr ""
"Seuraava vaihe on verkkokauppatilausten valmistelu varastossa. "
"Tilausmäärästä, täydennys- ja varastonhallintastrategioista tai "
"käytettävissä olevista resursseista riippuen voidaan toteuttaa erilaisia "
":doc:`varastonkäsittelyprosesseja vastaanottoihin ja toimituksiin </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations>"
"`. Näihin prosesseihin voi kuulua tuotteiden manuaalinen vastaanotto, "
":doc:`keräily </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"picking_methods>` ja :doc:`pakkaaminen </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack>`, "
":doc:`toimitusetikettien </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels>` tulostaminen ja tilausten "
":doc:`toimittaminen  <shipping>` asiakkaille, tai näiden prosessien "
"käsitteleminen :doc:`suoratoimituksen </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/dropshipping>` tai "
":doc:`konsignaatioprosessien </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations/owned_stock>` kautta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:119
msgid ""
"After completing the warehouse operations, return to the delivery order and "
"click :guilabel:`Validate` once the order has been shipped."
msgstr ""
"Varastotoimintojen suorittamisen jälkeen palaa toimitustilaukseen ja "
"napsauta :guilabel:`Vahvista`, kun tilaus on toimitettu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:123
msgid ""
"To enable automatic confirmation emails for completed delivery orders "
"(:guilabel:`Done` status), go to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration "
"--> Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Shipping` section, and "
"enable :guilabel:`Email Confirmation`."
msgstr ""
"Ottaaksesi käyttöön automaattiset vahvistussähköpostit valmiille "
"toimitustilauksille (tila :guilabel:`Valmis`), siirry kohtaan "
":menuselection:`Varastointi --> Asetukset --> Asetukset`, vieritä osioon "
":guilabel:`Toimitus` ja ota käyttöön :guilabel:`Sähköpostivahvistus`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:132
msgid ""
"To ensure that products ordered by customers are reserved in stock, go "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Operation Types`, click "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Orders` operation type, and set "
"the :guilabel:`Reservation Method` field to :doc:`At Confirmation </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"reservation_methods/at_confirmation>`. When enabled, product quantities are "
"automatically reserved once the order is confirmed, preventing items from "
"becoming unavailable after the order is placed."
msgstr ""
"Varmistaaksesi, että asiakkaiden tilaamat tuotteet varataan varastossa, "
"siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Varastointi --> Asetukset --> "
"Toimintotyypit`, napsauta toimintotyyppiä :guilabel:`Toimitustilaukset` ja "
"aseta kenttä :guilabel:`Varausmenetelmä` arvoon :doc:`Vahvistettaessa </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"reservation_methods/at_confirmation>`. Kun tämä on käytössä, tuotemäärät "
"varataan automaattisesti tilauksen vahvistamisen jälkeen, mikä estää "
"tuotteiden loppumisen tilauksen jättämisen jälkeen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:140
msgid ""
"If the customer pays by :ref:`wire transfer <payment_providers/bank_payments/"
"wire_transfer>`, products are not reserved in stock until the payment is "
"received and the order is manually confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Jos asiakas maksaa :ref:`tilisiirrolla <payment_providers/bank_payments/"
"wire_transfer>`, tuotteita ei varata varastossa ennen kuin maksu on "
"vastaanotettu ja tilaus vahvistetaan manuaalisesti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:145
msgid ":doc:`shipping`"
msgstr ":doc:`shipping`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:150
msgid "Returns and refunds"
msgstr "Palautukset ja hyvitykset"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:152
msgid ""
"Customers can :doc:`return </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/"
"returns>` products through the :doc:`customer portal </applications/general/"
"users/user_portals>` by navigating to the :guilabel:`Your Orders` section, "
"selecting the relevant order, and clicking the :guilabel:`Return` button. A "
"return document is automatically generated."
msgstr ""
"Asiakkaat voivat :doc:`palauttaa </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/"
"returns>` tuotteita :doc:`asiakasportaalin </applications/general/users/"
"user_portals>` kautta siirtymällä :guilabel:`Tilauksesi` -osioon, "
"valitsemalla kyseisen tilauksen ja napsauttamalla :guilabel:`Palauta` -"
"painiketta. Palautusasiakirja luodaan automaattisesti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:None
msgid "Return button in the portal."
msgstr "Palauta-painike portaalissa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:160
msgid ""
"Once the returned items are received, initiate the :doc:`return and refund "
"process </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns>` in the backend."
msgstr ""
"Kun palautetut tuotteet on vastaanotettu, aloita :doc:`palautus- ja "
"hyvitysprosessi </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns>` "
"taustajärjestelmässä."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:164
msgid ""
":doc:`Returning </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns>` "
"products may not be possible depending on the :doc:`product type </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/type>`."
msgstr ""
"Tuotteiden :doc:`palauttaminen </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/"
"returns>` ei välttämättä ole mahdollista :doc:`tuotetyypistä </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/type>` riippuen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:167
msgid ""
"To issue :doc:`refunds </applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/"
"credit_notes>`, the payment must have been made through a :ref:`refund-"
"compatible payment provider <payment_providers/supported_providers>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Hyvitysten </applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/"
"credit_notes>` myöntäminen edellyttää, että maksu on suoritettu "
":ref:`hyvityksiä tukevan maksupalveluntarjoajan <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>` kautta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:172
msgid ":doc:`/applications/services/helpdesk/advanced/after_sales`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:177
msgid "Invoicing"
msgstr "Laskutus"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:179
msgid ""
"The final step of an e-commerce order is generating and sending "
"the :doc:`customer invoice </applications/finance/accounting/"
"customer_invoices>`. Depending on your needs, invoices can be generated "
"manually or automatically."
msgstr ""
"Verkkokauppatilauksen viimeinen vaihe on :doc:`asiakaslaskun </applications/"
"finance/accounting/customer_invoices>` luominen ja lähettäminen. Tarpeidesi "
"mukaan laskut voidaan luoda manuaalisesti tai automaattisesti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:183
msgid "To automate invoicing:"
msgstr "Laskutuksen automatisointi:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:186
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section, enable :guilabel:`Automatic Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Ota :guilabel:`Verkkokauppa` -osiossa käyttöön :guilabel:`Automaattinen "
"lasku`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:187
msgid ""
"Select the relevant :guilabel:`Email Template`, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Valitse sopiva :guilabel:`Sähköpostipohja` ja napsauta sitten "
":guilabel:`Tallenna`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:188
msgid ""
"If needed, click the :icon:`fa-arrow-right` icon next to the template name "
"to customize the :doc:`email template </applications/general/companies/"
"email_template>`."
msgstr ""
"Tarvittaessa napsauta pohjan nimen vieressä olevaa :icon:`fa-arrow-right` -"
"kuvaketta mukauttaaksesi :doc:`sähköpostipohjaa </applications/general/"
"companies/email_template>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:192
msgid ""
"Customers can view their invoices under :guilabel:`Your Invoices` in "
"the :doc:`portal </applications/general/users/user_portals>`."
msgstr ""
"Asiakkaat voivat tarkastella laskujaan :guilabel:`Laskusi` -kohdassa "
":doc:`portaalissa </applications/general/users/user_portals>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:194
msgid ""
"Invoices are only sent automatically if (and when) the :doc:`payment </"
"applications/finance/payment_providers>` is registered."
msgstr ""
"Laskut lähetetään automaattisesti vain, jos (ja kun) :doc:`maksu </"
"applications/finance/payment_providers>` on rekisteröity."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:196
msgid ""
"When automatic invoicing is disabled and invoices are created manually, they "
"appear as :doc:`pro-forma invoices </applications/sales/sales/invoicing/"
"proforma>` in the customer portal until they are manually :ref:`sent to the "
"customer <accounting/invoice/sending>`."
msgstr ""
"Kun automaattinen laskutus on poistettu käytöstä ja laskut luodaan "
"manuaalisesti, ne näkyvät asiakasportaalissa :doc:`proforma-laskuina </"
"applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma>`, kunnes ne on manuaalisesti "
":ref:`lähetetty asiakkaalle <accounting/invoice/sending>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:201
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/payments`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/payments`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:202
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:203
msgid ""
"`Create a customer invoice from a sales order <https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=14AIEJ_B7rA>`_"
